b'Research Interests '
b'Molecular Beam Epitaxy of Compound Semiconductors and Multifunctional Oxides (BaTiO3, ZnO, HgCdTe, etc)'
b'fabrication of high-performance optoelectronic devices'
b'characterization HgCdTe detectors and avalanche photodiodes'
b'development of spintronic devices using nanowires and novel spin injectors'
b'Professional Achievements '
b'Best Paper Award, North American Molecular Beam Epitaxy Conference, Providence, 2001'
b'Best Paper Award, North American Molecular Beam Epitaxy Conference, Tempe, 2000'
b'Co-authored two book chapters: (a) \xe2\x80\x9cHigh-Speed Quantum Dot Lasers, P. Bhattacharya, S. Ghosh and T. Norris (b) \xe2\x80\x9cQuantum Dot Optoelectronic Devices\xe2\x80\x9d, P. Bhattacharya, S. Ghosh and A.D. Stiff-Roberts'
b'Authored 20 journal articles and more than 15 conference and invited papers'
b'Nominated for Best Graduate Student Instructor for College of Engineering, University of Michigan, 1999.'
b'Student Member IEEE, 1997-2003.'
b'Summer Research Fellowship, Indian Institute of Science, Bangalore, India, May 1997-July 1999'
